{"tid":44408,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"內地人用VISA及Master投保最多碌5,000美金","createTime":"2016-12-18T09:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T13:17:07.000Z","uid":2597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0db36a7a588816aa6d389750827f98afee88bc5a","tid":44408,"uid":2597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161218&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=56063290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161218%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D56063290&d=D6Tn%2B3Jic7I3saX6PoHa2hpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=3d85e668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161218%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D56063290&h=06b780dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161218&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=56063290</a><br />\n<br />\n早前市場誤傳VISA及Master卡於上周「被落閘」，內地客一度仍能使用上述兩張信用卡投保。不過，事隔一週，彭博引述消息指，內地客目前用VISA及Master卡投保，每份保單最多只能碌5,000美金，而且只限一次，意味不能分開數次碌卡以投保大額保單走資。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，外匯政策規定境外保險類商戶單筆交易，有不超過5,000美元或其他等值外幣的消費金額限制，本報亦從保險經紀口中證實，多間保險公司上週已先後通知代理及經紀將會嚴格落實上述限制，包括內地客生意最多的保誠及友邦。其中，保誠較早前口頭通知經紀，已於昨日下午1時30分起嚴格落實有關規定。有保險經紀亦稱，近日不少內地客趕尾班車，保誠及友邦投保中心均大排長龍<br />\n<br />\n雖然內地客目前的確可照用上述兩張信用卡投保，然而有「走資單」之稱、兼早於10月底已不接受銀聯卡付款的投資性壽險產品，保費難有5,000美金以內，故透過銀行卡投保走資此途等同正式全面落閘。<br />\n<br />\nVISA香港發言人表示，不評論市場傳聞，而Master卡則暫未有回覆相關查詢。<br />\n<br />\n保險界立法會議員陳健波指，自己暫未聽聞有關消息，未能評論對業界影響，但知道香港保險業監理處早前已向中國保險監督管理委員會反映，希望爭取以銀聯渠道繳付續保保費的彈性。<br />\n<br />\n《經濟參考報》早前曾引述消息指，外管局已要求VISA、Master卡等組織的境內發卡行，按照合規性、真實性的要求，執行金額限制類商戶的規定。不過值得注意的是，國內並不多人持有VISA、Master卡，即使閂閘影響遠不及銀聯，但分析相信對氣氛或有所打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfe85ced587b4b69a4dc73f5c7156acb8f7e6e8","tid":44408,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:20:04.000Z","msg":"D錢又會湧哂落樓市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw之前跌糟做保險班銀行仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58147ecabda1a3828469036bfb12c096af30947","tid":44408,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"開始鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431dad64c8a43ecac9fb0d7698f42353ca3d9971","tid":44408,"uid":49039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:32:11.000Z","msg":"感覺1299 好似幾年前既賭股咁"},{"pid":"7ec24c75d5dd8f638b758c83de39288d090467b5","tid":44408,"uid":67336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:45:31.000Z","msg":"保險狗抵能死"},{"pid":"7e2cc8594b66f6e94127ef068f9ecbec213c444f","tid":44408,"uid":61938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:28:03.000Z","msg":"我啲1299 Put 應該翻生喇掛"},{"pid":"19933f134d159b27809f4686a686ade5b0e2c1e1","tid":44408,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我啲1299 Put 應該翻生喇掛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c520dbe52888ace1c8c85106b17f0bc1540c564","tid":44408,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我啲1299 Put 應該翻生喇掛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快見$40<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451de9f6c06673db6027df47310058e56acd6fa7","tid":44408,"uid":61938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T15:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我啲1299 Put 應該翻生喇掛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"